  "decision_conditions": [
    "REASON: The proposed railings, by reason of their highly visible and prominent location would introduce an incongruous form of development that would result in clutter and be harmful to the character and appearance of the host building, the integrity of the terrace of which it forms part and the surrounding townscape. The proposal conflicts with policies 7.4 and 7.8 of the London Plan 2011, policies CS8 and CS9 of Islington’s Core Strategy 2011, policies D4, D5 and D11 of Islington's Unitary Development Plan 2002 and emerging policy DM1 of Islington’s Development Management Policies Submission Version 2012, Islington's Urban Design Guide (2006), and the NPPF 2012."
